elucidation of post-harvest 
physiology 

6. Other                       195,594                  184,243 

Total                          1,007,871                1,036,240 


<H3>  3. R&amp;D To Cope with Global Environmental and Tropical 
Agriculture Problems </H3>
  The MAFF will carry out R&amp;D that will contribute to 
solving 
global-scale environmental problems such as global warming, 
desertification, and the decline of tropical rainforests. 
  In addition, the MAFF will invite researchers from 
developing 
countries and will efficiently implement joint research on 
tropical agriculture. 


