<H3> <TI>   First Step Toward the 21st Century Infrastructure </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94FE0141A Tokyo NIKKEI COMMUNICATIONS in Japanese 4 Oct 93 p 
32-39--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94FE0141A </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo NIKKEI COMMUNICATIONS </F>


